296
00:39:41,256 --> 00:39:42,925
Would you go and find these boys,
please, Briony?

297
00:39:43,008 --> 00:39:44,718
Tell them dinner's ready,
and where are their manners?

298
00:39:44,801 --> 00:39:46,720
