-Briony, you'll do as you're told,

299
00:39:46,803 --> 00:39:49,306
or you'll go straight to your room.

300
00:40:18,418 --> 00:40:19,920
It's a letter!
-Give it to me!

301
00:40:20,003 --> 00:40:21,588
They've run away.
Who has?

302
00:40:21,672 --> 00:40:23,006
The twins.

303
00:40:23,924 --> 00:40:28,929
"We are going to run away because Lola
is so horrid to us and we want to go home.

304
00:40:30,597 --> 00:40:32,140
-"Also, there wasn't a play."
-Don't worry.

305
00:40:32,224 --> 00:40:34,476
We'll send out some search parties.
They can't have gone far.

306
00:40:34,560 --> 00:40:36,603
Cee, you come with me.

307
00:40:42,401 --> 00:40:43,485
Pierrot!

308
00:40:44,319 --> 00:40:45,404
Jackson!

309
00:40:46,613 --> 00:40:47,739
Boys!

310
