I mean, that's the point.

446
01:02:59,696 --> 01:03:03,116
We fight in France
and the French fucking hate us.

447
01:03:03,200 --> 01:03:06,370
Make me Home Secretary,
I'll sort this out in a fucking minute.

448
01:03:06,453 --> 01:03:08,956
